interface Loopback0
   mpls ldp interface
!
mpls ip
!
mpls ldp
   router-id interface Loopback0
   transport-address interface Loopback0
   neighbor hello-redundancy
   interface disabled default
   no shutdown
   !
   graceful-restart role speaker
      timer state-holding 500
      timer reconnect 500
!
router isis 100
   mpls ldp sync default